      <title>特朗普大选前夕，加拿大外商投资趋于稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/foreign-investment-into-canada-steadied-ahead-of-trump-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第三季度，加拿大的外国直接投资保持稳定，这是一个令人鼓舞的迹象，表明尽管美国大选前的不确定性加剧，但企业仍继续将资本留在这个北方国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/foreign-investment-into-canada-steadied-ahead-of-trump-election</guid>
